# Testing

Follow **Honeycomb** methodology. See [docs/TESTING.md](../../docs/TESTING.md) for full detail.

- **Unit**: Pure logic, utilities, domain rules.
- **Integration**: Use cases + repos, API + DB.
- **E2E**: Critical user journeys.

Choose the right type per scenario; no strict pyramid. Use descriptive names, prefer fakes/stubs over mocks, keep tests deterministic.
